{"tid":778683,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"屌你老母，乜撚野係black magic ?? 識玩的人一定係弱智","createTime":"2018-08-14T01:23:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-23T07:36:38.000Z","uid":53062,"like":9,"dislike":40,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"250fc31688c31c0b7a7e7ae328621353e7be0283","tid":778683,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T01:23:02.000Z","msg":"日頭都玩得好地地<br />\n有解手  斬手，可以拖下女仔手 (第一次拖好多手汗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\n去到夜晚玩房Game 好燥<br />\n所謂的房Game 係玩一晚black magic，完全唔知咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nABCD   A=1 B=2 C=3 D=?    好明顯係4，最後答案竟然係5  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />    <br />\n自問數學都算好，m2 有5*<br />\n之後出好多題都搵唔到邏輯，懷疑佢哋話岩就岩  錯就錯，個人已經燥燥地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n第二隻Game 玩拍蚊，又係冇邏輯，垃圾game <br />\n<br />\n之後玩嘭嘭嘭    數筆劃   Open close  心靈感應<br />\n全部估唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我中學讀書名列前茅，DSE best 5有29分，冇理由一個都諗唔到，所以我結論弱智先識得玩<br />\n<br />\n好撚燥又眼訓<br />\n於是話去訓覺<br />\n我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />    組爸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n時間凌晨三點鐘<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  完全唔知做乜    我訓覺算<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   ocamp 係唔會訓覺<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  下？  點可以唔訓覺<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  要訓覺你不如返屋企<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你哋慢慢玩，我返房先<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   你試下<br />\n我冇理佢，第二朝竟然冇叫醒我食早餐，仲問我點解咁遲起身<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nOcamp撚 我屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6031d